titlestmt.titleproper: Guide to the Annie Warburton Goodrich Papers
titlestmt.author: compiled by Staff of Manuscripts and Archives

profiledesc.creation: This finding aid was produced using ArchivesSpace on Saturday December 8, 2018 at 10:32

repository.corpname: Yale University. Department of Manuscripts and Archives

did.abstract: The papers consist of correspondence, photographs, nursing curriculum and memorabilia of Annie Warburton Goodrich. Also included are records of the Committee on Nursing Organization.

accessrestrict.head: Conditions Governing Access
accessrestrict.p: The materials are open for research.

prefercite.head: Preferred Citation
prefercite.p: Annie Warburton Goodrich Papers (MS 1308). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.

acqinfo.head: Immediate Source of Acquisition
acqinfo.p: Transferred from the Yale University Historical Medical Library, 1980.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: The papers consist of correspondence, photographs, nursing curriculum and memorabilia of Annie Warburton Goodrich. Also included are records of the Committee on Nursing Organization.

arrangement.head: Arrangement
arrangement.p: Arranged in two series: I. Correspondence and Papers. II. Photographs and Memorabilia.
